}Now imagine 30,000 of these.  Imagine this but with cross signing (that’s 30,000 * 2).  Imagine 30,000 of these with cross signing and proving that multiple conditions hold at once.  Imagine a supply chain worth of these things from all the entities that touch a component.  The scale of what we’re going to create is immense and will be, at the least, super-linear in growth.  This is going to be a big problem.  No matter h
